Adding Missing Components\
\
\ulnone To complete a request, Rails needs:\
\
1. Database table\
2. Route specifying which controller and action should handle requests for given URL\
3. A controller action to handle the request\
\
Steps to create action:\
\
1. Create table using \'93generate model\'94 command\
2. Run migration to add table to database\
3. Create route in \'93config > routes\'94 to connect URL to controller action\
4. Create controller using \'93generate controller\'94 command\
5. Create action in \'93app > controllers\'94\ul \
\
\
Fixing General Mistakes in Code\
\
\ulnone ** When error is shown at very end of the file (\'93end\'94 keyword), it usually means that an \'93end\'94 keyword is missing somewhere earlier in the file\ul \
