Fixing Problems with Views\
\
\ulnone - Console will list all files rendered when a new page is opened. If there is a problem with the view, you may edit these files\
- Views are made up of application-wide layout, page template, and partials\
- Use \'93find in files\'94 to find specific string in project that needs editing\ul \
\
\
